<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>예약 취소 관리</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">예약 취소 관리</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">모든 예약을 조회하고 취소할 수 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <form action="/admin/reservation-list" method="GET" class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center bg-slate-50 gap-4">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <button type="submit" name="status" value="ALL" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-slate-800 text-white">전체</button>
                    <button type="submit" name="status" value="RESERVED" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600">예약</button>
                    <button type="submit" name="status" value="RECEIVED" class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600">접수</button>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <i data-lucide="search" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                        <input type="text" name="keyword" value="" placeholder="환자명 검색..." class="pl-9 pr-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none w-64"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>

            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                <thead>
                    <tr class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium">시간</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium">환자명</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium">연락처</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium">진료과 / 전문의</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium">상태</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium text-right">액션</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
                    <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">10:00</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">김환자</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">010-1234-5678</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">내과 / 김의사</td>
                        <td class="p-4">
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-blue-100 text-blue-800">예약</span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-right">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2">
                                <form action="/admin/reservation-list" method="POST" class="inline" onsubmit="return confirm('예약을 취소하시겠습니까?');">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="1">
                                    <button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-red-50 text-red-600 hover:bg-red-100 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
                                        <i data-lucide="x-circle" class="w-4 h-4"></i> 취소
                                    </button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="p-4 border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 flex justify-center">
                <nav class="flex gap-2"><span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded">1</span><a href="?page=2" class="px-3 py-1 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded">2</a></nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>lucide.createIcons();</script>
</body>
</html>